title: Omni performs "Plastic Pyramid" and more Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Omni performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded June 25, 2024.

Songs:
INTL Waters 00:37
Forever Beginner 03:54
All I Wanna Do 06:10
Compliment 09:30
Plastic Pyramid Feat. Hannah D'Amato 13:40

Philip Frobos - Vocals, Bass
Frankie Broyles - Guitar, Keyboard
Chris Yonker - Drums
Hannah D’Amato (Ham) - Guest Vocals from Fake Fruit

Host: Troy Nelson
Audio Engineer: Julian Martlew
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Ettie Wahl
Editor: Luke Knecht
